overview.en: As a new industry, 99x is committed to public welfare activities and community construction, which is fully reflected in the difficult times. With the determination of unity, we will create an ecosystem cycle with our own actions, and implement the Natasha plan with the whole network revenue, then we will take 99x as the user's pass to ensure that users can be guaranteed under the circumstances of non resistance. In the later stage, we will unify the cooperative merchants and use 90% of the whole network revenue The construction of cooperation Hospital School Red Cross, etc., allows users to live a peaceful life, and users can understand the operation easily.
overview.zh: 99X作为一个新兴产业，立志于公益活动和社区建设，充分体现在困难时期，众志成城的决心，用自己的行动打造生态系统循环，用全网收益实行Natasha计划，则将99X作为用户的通行证，确保用户在非抗拒情况下，得到保障，后期将统一合作商户，用全网收益的 90% 建设合作医院学校红十字等，让用户可以安心的生活，用户在操作的时候通俗易懂。
